import Layout from "./Layout"
import Login from "./Login"

import { BrowserRouter,Routes, Route, Link } from "react-router-dom"

function App(){
  return(

    <BrowserRouter>
      <Routes>
        <Route path='/'    element={<Layout/>}></Route>
        <Route path='/login'    element={<Login/>}></Route>
      </Routes>
    </BrowserRouter>

  )
}

export default App
